{"title_page": "The Very One Stakes (Gulfstream Park)", "text_new": "{{about|the thoroughbred horse race held at [[Gulfstream Park]]|the thoroughbred horse race with similar name at [[Pimlico Race Course]]|The Very One Stakes (Pimlico)}}\n{{Infobox horseraces\n| surface       = Turf \n| class         = Grade III\n| horse race    = The Very One Stakes\n| image         =\n| caption       =\n| location      = [[Gulfstream Park]]<br>[[Hallandale Beach, Florida]],<br> [[United States]]\n| inaugurated   = 1984 \n| race type     = [[Thoroughbred]] - [[Flat racing]] - Turf\n| website       = [https://www.gulfstreampark.com/ Gulfstream Park]\n| distance      = {{frac|1|3|16}} miles \n| track         = Left-handed\n| qualification = [[filly|fillies]] and [[mares]], four years old and older  \n| weight        = Assigned\n| purse         = [[United States dollar|$]]150,000 (2020)\n| bonuses       =\n}}\n'''The Very One Stakes''' is a [[Graded stakes race|Grade III]] American [[Thoroughbred horse race]] for [[filly|fillies]] and [[mares]] that are four years or older, over a distance of {{frac|1|1|16}} miles on the [[grass|turf]] {{frac|1|3|16}} miles on the [[grass|turf]] held annually in late February or early March at [[Gulfstream Park]], [[Hallandale Beach, Florida]].  The event currently carries a purse of $150,000. \n\n==History== \nThe race was inaugurated in May 1987<ref name=Pedigree>{{cite web|url=https://www.pedigreequery.com/index.php?query_type=stakes&search_bar=stakes&field=view&id=967 |title=THE VERY ONE STAKES - MULTIPLE TRACKS |work=Thoroughbred Pedigree Online |date=2020 |accessdate=25 April 2020}}</ref> and named after the winning mare '''[[The Very One]]'''<ref name=mare>{{cite web|url=https://www.pedigreequery.com/index.php?query_type=horse&search_bar=horse&h=THE+VERY+ONE&g=5&cellpadding=0&small_font=1&l= |title=THE VERY ONE (USA) b. M, 1975 - 71 Starts, 22 Wins, 12 Places, 8 Shows Career Earnings: $1,030,120 |work=Thoroughbred Pedigree Online |date=2020 |accessdate=25 April 2020}}</ref> who won 22 races in her career including the [[Graded stakes race|Grade I]] [[Santa Barbara Handicap]]. The event was not held in 1988 and 1989.<ref name=Equibase>{{cite web|url=http://www.equibase.com/profiles/Results.cfm?type=Stakes&stkid=523 |title= The Very One Stakes (Gr. 3) |work=Equibase |date=2020 |accessdate=25 April 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe event was initially named the The Very One Handicap<ref name=Equibase/>and was predominantly run at {{frac|1|3|8}} miles <ref name=Equibase/> but was shortened to the current distance of {{frac|1|3|16}} miles in 2016.<ref name=Equibase/>\n\n==Records==\n'''Speed record:''' \n*Current distance: {{frac|1|3|16}} miles  1:51.40  - Suffused ([[Great Britain|GB]]) (2017)\n*Former distance: {{frac|1|3|8}} miles  2:11.71 - Honey Rider (2005)\n\n'''Margins:''' \n* {{frac|9|1|2}} lengths &ndash; Bungalow (1992)\n\n;Most wins by a [[jockey]]\n* 5 - [[Jerry D. Bailey]] (1990, 1994 1996, 2001, 2002)\n\n;Most wins by a [[Horse trainer|trainer]]\n* 7 - [[Christophe Clement]] (1998, 1999, 2001, 2002, 2007, 2008, 2015)\n\n==Winners==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Winner\n! Age\n! Jockey\n! Trainer\n! Owner\n! Distance\n! Time\n! Purse\n! Grade\n! Ref\n|-style=\"font-size:90%; background-color:white\"\n|align=\"left\" colspan=11|'''The Very One Stakes'''\n|-style=\"font-size:90%; background-color:lightcyan\"\n|align=center |2020\n| Elizabeth Way ([[Ireland|IRE]])\n|align=center | 4\n| [[Paco Lopez]]\n| [[Roger L. Attfield]]\n| John J. McCormack\n|align=center | {{frac|1|3|16}} miles\n|align=center | 1:54.26\n|align=center |$150,000\n|align=center |3\n|<ref name=R2020>{{cite web|url=http://www.equibase.com/premium/eqbPDFChartPlus.cfm?RACE=7&BorP=P&TID=GP&CTRY=USA&DT=02/29/2020&DAY=D&STYLE=EQB |title=2020 The Very One Stakes Grade 3 - (race 7) |work=Equibase |date=29 February 2020 |accessdate=25 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-style=\"font-size:90%; background-color:lightcyan\"\n|align=center |2019\n| Holy